This program reproduces Fig. 11 in:
I. Hayut, B.W. Connors, E.E. Fanselow and D. Golomb,
LTS and FS inhibitory interneurons, short-term synaptic plasticity, and 
cortical circuit dynamics
PLoS Comput. Biol. 7(10): e1002248.

Files:
dyn_all.com           Command procedure that runs the program.
dyn_all.gr            XMGrace parameter file for plotting the figure.
Makefile       
rlf.c  rlfn.c         Program Files of C program.
rlf.h rlfn.h rlfa.h   Header files for C program.
nr.c                  Functions from NUmerical Recipes.
nr.h                  Header file for functions from NUmerical Recipes.
rlf.n.d4              Data file for panel A.
rlf.n.d1              Data file for panel B.
rlf.n.d2              Data file for panel C.
rlf.n.d5              Data file for panel D.


To run the program on a Linux machine with XMGrace graphics software, use
the commands:

make rlf
./dyn_all.com
